      "description": "This E46 M3 features the legendary S54B32 naturally aspirated inline-six, delivering linear power through six individual throttle bodies and a high-precision 6-speed manual transmission. The chassis remains taut with a factory-spec limited-slip differential and optimized suspension kinematics. Maintained with a focus on mechanical integrity, the VANOS system has been serviced, and the subframe has been inspected for structural soundness. It is a mechanically robust driver\u2019s example with a crisp 8,000 RPM redline, offering an analog connection to the road that modern vehicles lack. The exterior and interior show honest wear consistent with a well-loved performance machine, but the powertrain remains the focal point of this visceral driving platform.",
