      "description": "Offered is a mechanically sound E46 M3 powered by the high-revving S54B32 inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a recently recalibrated dual-VANOS system for optimal cam phasing. The drivetrain is anchored by a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission with a firm clutch take-up and precise gate selection. Significant preventative maintenance has been performed, including a comprehensive rear subframe reinforcement and the installation of polyurethane bushings to eliminate deflection under lateral load. The factory limited-slip differential provides consistent lock-up, and the suspension maintains its original geometry with refreshed dampers. While the exterior reflects its status as a dedicated driver\u2019s car, the mechanical vitals\u2014from oil pressure to cooling system integrity\u2014are within factory tolerances. A robust, enthusiast-maintained example ready for technical roads.",
